## What Are Elite Campaigns?

Elite Campaigns are advanced versions of the standard campaigns that feature stronger enemies, stricter roster requirements, and significantly better rewards.

While they are more difficult than normal campaigns, they are among the most valuable long-term progression systems in Tacticus.

## Why Elite Campaigns Matter

Elite Campaigns offer improved farming efficiency for many of the resources players need most.

Benefits include:

* Better drop rates on upgrade materials
* More efficient energy usage
* Access to additional character shards
* Faster long-term account progression

For many veteran players, Elite Campaigns become the primary destination for daily energy spending.

## The Investment Challenge

Unlike normal campaigns, Elite Campaigns require substantial investment in the campaign's core characters.

Many players struggle because they either:

* Underinvest and hit progression walls
* Overinvest and spend resources inefficiently

The goal of this guide is to identify the minimum practical investment needed to clear each campaign while avoiding unnecessary upgrades.

## How to Use This Guide

Each campaign section lists the recommended investment levels for the required characters.

Use these recommendations as a starting point rather than an absolute requirement.

Factors such as badges, equipment, active abilities, passive abilities, and battle strategy can all influence the exact investment needed.

## Long-Term Strategy

Do not feel pressured to complete every Elite Campaign immediately.

Focus first on the campaigns that unlock the characters, upgrade materials, and farming locations that will provide the greatest value to your account.

Steady progress across multiple campaigns is often more effective than trying to force a single campaign to completion.

